      "id": "col1_text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 110,
      "height": 171,
      "text": "Purpose:\nUser identity, role,\npreferences\n\nExample:\n\"数据工程师, 熟悉dbt\"\n\"用户偏好中文回复\"\n\nLifetime:\nLong-term, rarely\nchanges\n\nToken priority: LOW",
