    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "col2_text",
      "x": 180,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 110,
      "height": 171,
      "text": "Purpose:\nHow to approach work;\nwhat to avoid / keep\n\nExample:\n\"复杂图表用 Excalidraw\n而非 HTML/CSS\"\n\"Don't auto-summarize\ndiffs\"\n\nLifetime:\nMedium-term,\nproject-specific\n\nToken priority: HIGH",
