      "x": 480,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 110,
      "height": 171,
      "text": "Purpose:\nPointers to external\nsystems, docs, APIs\n\nExample:\n\"pipeline bugs tracked\nin Linear 'INGEST'\"\n\"MCP server config\nformat\"\n\nLifetime:\nMedium-long term,\nuntil systems change\n\nToken priority:\nMedium",
